  "worklog": "## 2026-03-30 04:28 UTC \u2014 [Pillar 4] Regime Classifier Built + Fear & Greed Alpha Signal\n\n**Task:** Build BTC regime classifier for alpha research pipeline. Analyze Fear & Greed correlation. Wire new data source into confidence scoring.\n\n**Finding:**\n1. **Built `regime_classifier.py`** \u2014 standalone module that classifies BTC into 4 regimes using 5-min candle data:\n   - `RANGE` \ud83c\udfaf \u2014 PM contrarian trades work best (low vol, mean-reverting)\n   - `TREND` \ud83d\udcc8 \u2014 directional, orderly moves (PM risky, filter/reduce)\n   - `HIGH_VOL` \u26a1 \u2014 extreme moves (DO NOT trade PM)\n   - `CRASH_RECOVERY` \ud83d\udd04 \u2014 post-crash V-bounce (HL long bias signal)\n   - Uses: avg range, max range, volume ratio, net change, directional consistency\n   - Current output: TREND (UP), score 5/10, PM not tradeable \u274c\n\n2. **Crash anatomy (22:40-22:45 UTC Sunday):**\n   - 22:40: 0.95% range, 443 BTC \u2192 $66,255\u2192$65,684\n   - 22:45: 1.04% range, 933 BTC \u2192 $65,684\u2192$65,046 (cascade bottom)\n   - 22:50-23:00: V-bounce $65,046\u2192$66,036\n   - 00:15: Monster spike 1.72% range, 328 BTC \u2192 $65,853\u2192$66,909\n   - Total: $65,046\u2192$67,468 = +3.7% recovery in 6 hours\n\n3. **Fear & Greed Index: 8/100 (Extreme Fear)** \u2014 10+ consecutive days of Extreme Fear (range 8-14). Our entire W13 profit (+$216, 55% WR) was generated during this fear regime. Contrarian 5-min binary strategy + Extreme Fear = edge amplifier.\n\n**My thinking:** The Fear & Greed signal is macro-level alpha. During Extreme Fear, retail panics and overreacts on 5-min timeframes \u2014 exactly what our contrarian bias-fading strategy exploits. The regime classifier gives us micro-level (5-min) regime detection. Together: Fear&Greed < 20 = boost PM trade confidence by 5-10%, Fear&Greed > 70 = reduce confidence (greed = less overreaction to fade).\n\n**Decision:**\n- `regime_classifier.py` is built and tested. Ready to wire into bot as import.\n- **V4 enhancement queued:** Add F&G API call at bot startup, use as confidence modifier:\n  - F&G \u2264 15: +10% confidence boost (contrarian edge amplified)\n  - F&G 15-30: +5% boost\n  - F&G 30-70: neutral\n  - F&G \u2265 70: -10% (reduce size, less overreaction to fade)\n- Don't deploy at 4 AM \u2014 queue for Monday active hours when we can monitor.\n\n**Next P4 heartbeat:** Wire regime_classifier into bot's should_trade() as supplementary signal. Add F&G API lookup at session start. Backtest F&G correlation against all 277 trades in trades.jsonl.\n\n## 2026-03-30 04:23 UTC \u2014 [Pillar 3] STRONG_TREND Rally Analysis + PM Bot Crash Fix\n\n**Task:** Analyze current BTC regime and its implications for strategy. PM bot had crashed again \u2014 diagnose and fix. Check HL positions.\n\n**Finding:**\n1. **BTC rallied from $65,000 \u2192 $67,468** since 22:00 UTC Sunday. Classic V-shaped recovery: liquidation cascade at 22:00 (2,219 BTC volume \u2014 7x normal), then steady grind up. +3.8% off the low. Current regime: STRONG_TREND (UP).\n\n2. **PM bot crashed at ~01:03 UTC** \u2014 process died silently (no error in logs). Restarted at 04:09, died again within 20 seconds. Second restart",
